content: Greetings Fans of ChatGPT!Today we announce the start of the ChatGPT bounty campaign.Total reward is 42 000 $ChatGPT. Campaing duration is 2 weeks!The rules are very simple:Follow our TwitterJoin our Telegram chatPost 1 message to our Telegram chat every dayPost 1 comment to our Twitter every dayMake 1 post in this Bitcointalk thread every dayComments should be at least 150 symbols length, and yes you can generate them using ChatGPT20% of the reward will go to bounty manager who will be chosen from bounty participants. Who wants, write me in PM.Rest 80% will be distributed between bounty participants proportional to the number of participation days.  Reward will be distributed after 30 days of starting trading on DEX.------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Apply for Bounty now:https://forms.gle/1NuaWwo2TtRiaFSf9------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------Also check-out our Web-site https://chatgpt-fancommunity.org/White paper https://chatgpt-fancommunity.org/white-paper/Tokenomics https://chatgpt-fancommunity.org/tokenomics/Audit https://github.com/Audit-Ace/Audits-Smart-Contracts/blob/main/ChatGPT%20Audit%20Report.pdfTwitter https://twitter.com/ChatGPT_FansTelgram Chat https://t.me/ChatGPTFans$ChatGPT is a Fan token of The Unofficial ChatGPT Fan CommunityThe ChatGPT Fan Community is a dedicated group of fans of ChatGPT ChatBot, a powerful language model developed by OpenAI. To show our support, the community has created a cryptocurrency token known as the ChatGPT Fan Token, which is a BEP-20 token on the Binance blockchain. This token, named after ChatGPT, serves as a symbol of the community’s admiration for the chatbot.
